posts.post_title: Miscut T206 and Factory 42 NC coupon $39 dlvd+ Bonus!

posts.post_content: Miscut card graded 2.5 and the 1914 Factory 42 NC coupon. $40 dlvd. Coupon has a couple baseball related tobacco names on the back, Catchers Mitt and Base Ball League. On the back of the card, you can see the lines on the right from a second Piedmont back
$39 now for the Murray, the coupon and as a miscut bonus, a 1986 Topps Dale Berra with a miscut back that shows about 40% of the back of Bobby Clark's card
